$ C:\Users\username\AppData\Local\Temp\wsl-crashes\

→ Windows/Subsystem-for-Linux[WSL] 2.3.17 stores core dumps by default in `C:\Users\username\AppData\Local\Temp\wsl-crashes\`.
-
The folder can be changed by setting `crashDumpFolder` under the section `[wsl2]` in `→ Windows/dirs/Users/username/_wslconfig`.
-
Setting `MaxCrashDumpCount` to `-1`  enables the generation of core dumps for WSL.


sa:


